90
00:11:23,361 --> 00:11:25,121
I suddenly, no, good.

91
00:11:25,361 --> 00:11:28,080
I remember something that I thought to myself.

92
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:33,681
The table isn't, of course, a kind of special relationship to tables like this.

93
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:36,321
It means food.

94
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:46,801
It means being concerned to make good meals and to take the trouble to get the meal set up and cook the food and get the people together.

95
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:49,521
I did talk about it in some other connection, didn't I?

96
00:11:49,521 --> 00:11:50,801
