00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:43,481
The example of it is the Samuel Enderby, the ship, where he meets Boomer and Bunger, the two happy captain and ship's doctor, which who live in an ordinary, sort of happy, seeming kind of domestic or whatever, I mean, friendly, no, it's a really friendly mood.

